properties.description:
The connector is for email sending by MailJet API. You can send email with attachment which can be URL or base64 content and send email to multiple recepients.
For prettier look and feel of email, MailJet also allows you to use MailJet template with override variables.

201.description: Created The POST request was successfully executed.

204.description: No Content  No content found or expected to return. Returned when DELETE was successful.

304.description: The PUT request didn't affect any record.

400.description: One or more parameters are missing or maybe mispelled (unknown resource or action)

401.description: You have specified an incorrect Api Key / API Secret Key. You may be unauthorized to access the API or your API key may be expired.

403.description: You are not authorised to access this resource.

429.description: Oops! You have reach the maximum number of calls allowed per minute by our API. Please review your integration to reduce the number of call issued by your system.

500.description: Ouch! Something went wrong on our side and we apologize! When such error occurs, it will contain an error identifier in it's description (e.g. 'ErrorIdentifier' : 'D4DF574C-0C5F-45C7-BA52-7AA8E533C3DE'), which is crucial for us to track the problem and identify the root cause.
